    <text><group><text type="letter" xml:lang="ru" xml:id="letter-01121">
        <body>
            <opener>
            <salute rend="inline">
               <persName ref="people.xml#pan01">Никита
                        Иванович!</persName>
            </salute>
         </opener>
            <p>Приложенныя два <seg xml:lang="fr">mémoires,</seg> подал Бискуп <placeName ref="places.xml#vil01">Виленской</placeName> брату Вашему, на которые он письмом
                ответствовать будет, что я приказла отослать к Министрам, не обещая и не отказывая;
                а помнится; что Огинский о том же просил; а другое, кажется, лутче в то не
                ввязываться, дабы большинство голосов не в моду у них вошло,и для того отослать к
                    <persName ref="people.xml#key03">Графу Кайзерлингу,</persName> дабы он умненько
                сие от меня отклонил. Я в шестом часу сегодня отселе поеду к Вам в <placeName ref="places.xml#pet01">Петербург</placeName> чрез <placeName ref="places.xml#gos01">Гостилицы</placeName> и <placeName ref="places.xml#pet02">Петергоф,</placeName> а Вы с <persName ref="people.xml#pau01">Великим
                    Князем</persName> в город к моему приезду приезжайте; я, отдохнув дни с два в
                    <placeName ref="places.xml#pet02">Петергофе,</placeName> в город думаю быть.</p>
            <closer>
            <signed>
               <persName ref="people.xml#cat01">Екатерина.</persName>
            </signed>
            <lb/>
                <dateline>Изъ <placeName ref="places.xml#rig01">Риги</placeName>.<lb/>
                    <date when-custom="1764-07-15">15 числа Іюля,<lb/>
                1764.</date>
            </dateline>
         </closer>
        </body>
    </text>
    <text type="translation" xml:lang="en" xml:id="letter-01121-en">
        <body>
            <opener>
                <salute rend="inline">
                    <persName ref="people.xml#pan01">Nikita Ivanovich!</persName>
                </salute>
            </opener>
            <p>The two attached <seg xml:lang="fr">mémoires</seg> were submitted by the Bishop of 
                <placeName ref="places.xml#vil01">Vilnius</placeName> to your brother. He will respond to them by 
                letter, as I have instructed that they be forwarded to the Ministers, without making 
                any promise or refusal. I recall that Oginsky also made a similar request; but the other 
                matter, I believe, is better not to become involved in, so that the majority vote does 
                not become fashionable among them. Therefore, it should be referred to 
                <persName ref="people.xml#key03">Count Keyserling</persName>, so that he might, with 
                some tact, deflect it on my behalf. At six o’clock today I shall travel from here to 
                <placeName ref="places.xml#pet01">Petersburg</placeName> via 
                <placeName ref="places.xml#gos01">Gostilitsy</placeName> and 
                <placeName ref="places.xml#pet02">Peterhof</placeName>; and you, together with the 
                <persName ref="people.xml#pau01">Grand Duke</persName>, should come to the city 
                to meet my arrival. I intend to rest for a couple of days in 
                <placeName ref="places.xml#pet02">Peterhof</placeName> and then proceed to the city.</p>
            <closer>
                <signed>
                    <persName ref="people.xml#cat01">Catherine</persName>
                </signed>
                <lb/>
                <dateline>From <placeName ref="places.xml#rig01">Riga</placeName>.<lb/>
                    <date when-custom="1764-07-15">15th of July,<lb/>1764.</date>
                </dateline>
            </closer>
        </body>
    </text>
